{"h7298e855ga931g4fa5ga362g8ed82d535005": ["Well! Look what the rat dragged in.", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "448516bc-0b30-fcd2-340c-30576324a743"], "hd89e0dbbg6427g4bb8gb3cdg007d3d8fe8f2": ["Well! Look who's gettin' dragged back. And by such high company! How badly did you mess up?", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "448516bc-0b30-fcd2-340c-30576324a743"], "hc19261ccg541eg49d6g95f9gdb4fc44bb19a": ["Can it! I know something Ragzlin will want to hear.", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "2cdac6c8-afb6-ec03-2039-a7e4a785ad3f"], "h242e466egb8e3g4eedgbf65g48301d0c42b4": ["Yeah? What's that?", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "9f9d363e-b8ac-4f40-ef7d-bb596dd00bc3"], "h70279326g4672g40c2g8abfg600cddc7fc59": ["I been in some druid's grove. This one sprang me. Now - move over, so I can tell Ragzlin myself!", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "65d67dc6-45c1-996d-2361-9fa7524024de"], "h842f8640gb5c0g4385g83f1g8e0604cb94df": ["Hold on. Where are the raiders?", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "a59fa30d-7071-c796-d46f-e7ccf4b5ae9d"], "h763519d5g9f4dg4f2egb394g6ab66db49b4a": ["Dead. Every last one.", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "c5ddc1cf-22ea-6e68-69aa-b64017d144b3"], "h3eda0b87g0114g49e7g9f49g8c2f1d10c038": ["Ragzlin's other drow friend won't be happy to hear <i>that.</i>", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "9ef9ce55-365b-32a2-e341-658f05a8fd69"], "h54fb7748g43b0g4d94g8db8gee0e34106b83": ["Ragzlin's drow friend won't be happy to hear <i>that.</i>", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "9ef9ce55-365b-32a2-e341-658f05a8fd69"], "h40e7223bgfd28g4e50g9ea9gc9ef0583a25b": ["She'll be happy enough when I tell her where them looters is holin' up. Let me through.", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "3c17ae63-1698-26d3-eb93-6839c8ba05c8"], "h2d4dbbf1gd4eag4e31gb9ddg677a87c0eb6e": ["Go on. I ain't gonna hold up a drow.", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "22babc05-de03-d098-2e71-40f50bbceae3"], "h10e5cc10g902bg434cg8d97gc16e81a91428": ["C'mon! Gotta let the drow True Soul know where them looters is. We'll be heroes!", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "7f6f4ca9-1b3a-6dee-5385-43a6ca66c5b3"], "h10adeb2dg5fcbg4a5dg92c2g621eb09d3810": ["Hold on, now.", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "da23928f-1413-af14-c714-e9cdc5f304bc"], "h3fb7693eg723eg4540ga4fbge41b001a4aa8": ["Is it true, what Saz says? You helped her escape that grove?", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "cbb8d91b-3680-630c-764d-2dc3b5be34b6"], "hc353ebfeg7826g4332gbb34g57b078915179": ["Yes - I don't believe in keeping prisoners.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "20d8d969-5b75-c79a-fd35-cb106556ee41"], "h9f55e0d4g95a8g4743g892dg976de0c17192": ["Heh. Then behave while you're inside. Our people don't mind it one bit.", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "b29508d9-7eec-32c8-e671-979995fc3079"], "h0dd02f0cgb925g4f48gb768g27cbdc07a355": ["That's enough outta you.", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "1a62b995-4a73-b5fd-13f8-b6b3c15d9a01"], "h64a531f9g0a72g4dddg8191gc9192538811c": ["C'mon! Gotta let the drow know where them looters is. We'll be heroes!", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "a6d09170-be44-4a16-d0d1-7d5da9cb113b"], "hd862d9a3g7a8cg4737gad85g732605fae46a": ["Just hoping she'll prove useful.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "2bd92974-2797-4606-915b-ab632e99009f"], "h9517077ag4abbg44bagaf47g2464db7147a1": ["Behave yourself. Saz's vouchin' for you. You mess up, you <i>and </i>Saz'll get it.<i></i>", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "3c4171c7-3930-a7ef-1445-b41d863187f3"], "h90d00019g858bg4c09g97f3g7bdc19172917": ["<i>Shrug and say nothing.</i>", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "5f8aade8-0552-8d56-30ae-8368ef0d040b"], "hf014c833g13fcg4f00gbabcgc33f2ced3ba1": ["Quiet type, eh? Good. Keep outta trouble, or you <i>and </i>Saz'll get it.", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "118035c0-9bbb-2d1a-8cfa-05c284354d29"], "h97345a9bgca19g4569gb7e2ga84f3bdc8657": ["I'm only keeping her around in case I get hungry.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "deab7496-bb67-aea2-0e3e-59a7c651148d"], "h8c9d1081gc8ebg4f14ga2d2ge0d4b202c430": ["My reasons are of no concern to you.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "2d36f833-e11d-0c27-ca11-a8fd4e5cf644"], "he66e9b21gfc24g4e4cg86f2g77286826422f": ["True enough. I couldn't resist her charming company.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "044f61df-1a9e-9350-7f1d-ed51554e74b2"], "h0c7aaeeag3716g4a37gad40g6dfbd469edd3": ["I enjoy making new friends.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "971f1852-ef4c-4685-08ca-67f495f1e957"], "h8bd5e567g3f45g4f21gb2cbgbf50be2e82e3": ["I just hate seeing animals in cages.", "e0d1ff71-04a8-4340-ae64-9684d846eb83", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "0e7dff00-b4fb-2ccc-1a72-bad984b07738"], "h50ee23fag7046g47b9gbab5g6e00f653a9ce": ["Go on ahead. Already met your little friend. Two of you can go celebrate together.", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "c43581b1-7a10-d35b-6a0d-82553520f02f"], "h1fd4d744g19acg45f0g8b5cg9748bf5a81b1": ["C'mon! Gotta let the drow know where them looters is. We'll be heroes!", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "dbce8523-0732-2d45-f05c-761fb03522fc"], "h671beae6g8d4ag4ea1g8473gf9a52af5c8bd": ["I ain't gonna hold up a True Soul.", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "3f114a42-3e6a-ee03-8795-a4e4bd20c992"], "h309ae893g5676g421fgab96g00da908c303a": ["C'mon! Gotta let the drow know where them looters is. We'll be heroes!", "783d7572-a846-455f-b686-247a95263ebb", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "07c79e11-7764-4992-cfd8-4d217bdffbf6"], "h2a891490gab18g471fg9653g2091a6dfdc0b": ["How'd a rat like you get in with a True Soul?", "6d69a347-9b3f-4b64-818e-013f849c6ae4", ".\\dialogs\\Act1\\Goblin\\GOB_Checkpoint_ThreeWayDialogWithCapturedGoblin.html", "ddf2ef11-41e6-095f-a55c-2e3de26b6f5f"]}